Name: Bath Salts
Kind: Drug Epidemic
Location: United States
Time: 2003-present
Human Impact: 68 reported deaths in the U.S.
Economic Impact: Little
Resources Needed: Police/DEA investigations, clinics for treatment, Awareness groups
Ways to Help: Clinic Volunteers, Joining an awareness group
