Name: Global Financial Crisis
Kind: Global Depression
Location: Global
Time: 2007-present
Human Impact: Large-scale unemployment, Average work week reduced to 33 hours in U.S
Economic Impact: Recession, widening of the wealth gap
Resources Needed: Economic stimulus, federal regulation of banking/Wall Street
Ways to Help: Awareness, smart investing
