----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Name: Tibetan Occupation
Kind: Cultural Genocide
Location: Tibet
Time: 1950's-present
Human Impact: Mass suicides, Cultural genocide, Death toll estimated to be around 1,200,000
Economic Impact: An economic boom in Tibet, with a 65x increase in Tibet's GDP before occupation
Resources Needed: Donations to Tibetan awareness organizations
Ways to Help: Join an awareness organization, donate to Free Tibet, boycott goods made in China
Embedded Images: 
	Image 1: http://ligress.files.wordpress.com/2009/04/tibet_map.gif
	Image 2: http://worldsfamousphotos.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/04/budist_monk_on_fire.jpg
Embedded Videos: http://www.youtube.com/embed/bWnfJqqW2Yk
